Class Summary
DbaseFileHeader Represents the header of a Dbase III file.
DbaseFileReader Reads Dbase III files.
DbaseFileWriter Used to write Dbase III files.
DbaseFileWriter.FieldFormatter Utility for formatting Dbase fields.
NumberParser Various number parsing utilities.
ShapefileReader Readers an ESRI shapefile and populates a GeoMap object with its features and attributes.
ShapefileWriter Writes out a geoMap object as a collection of ESRI shapefiles.
 

Package org.gicentre.geomap.io Description

Utilities for reading and writing various file formats

This package includes general utilities for reading and writing various file formats. In particular it contains classes for reading and creating shapefiles.
